1.title: Episode #1.1
1.plot: MMA legend Bas Rutten joins fight expert Kenny Rice to provide all the latest news, highlights, analysis and rankings.

2.title: Episode #1.2
2.plot: Inside MMA goes on the road to Las Vegas where hosts Bas Rutten and Kenny Rice provide news, highlights, expert analysis, and more.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Hosts Bas Rutten and Kenny Rice Weekly bring you news, highlights, rankings, "Smack Track" statistics and more.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: This week's Inside MMA features an Iraqi War veteran who now does his fighting in the ring. And in "Fight Club" we visit a popular training center.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Hosts Bas Rutten and Kenny Rice bring you all the latest mixed martial arts news, highlights, and rankings.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: Hosts Kenny Rice and Bas Rutten provide MMA news, highlights, latest rankings and more.

7.title: Episode #1.7
7.plot: Kenny Rice and Bas Rutten host the show that MMA fans cannot miss. Special guests include FIGHT! Magazine editor Donovan Craig, undefeated MMA Lightweight Chris "the Polish Hammer" Horodecki, and former MMA Heavyweight Champion Vladimir Matyushenko.

8.title: Episode #1.8
8.plot: Hosts Kenny Rice and HDNet Fights commissioner Guy Mezger provide a preview of the IFL Grand Prix. Also Ron Kruck has an exclusive interview with MMA Heavyweight Matt Lindland and the guest panel includes actor Ray Romano and #4 ranked Light Heavyweight Rameau Thierry Sokoudjou.

9.title: Episode #1.9
9.plot: Hosts Bas Rutten and Kenny Rice bring you the latest ranking, highlights and top news stories in mixed martial arts.

10.title: Episode #1.10
10.plot: Hosts Bas Rutten and Kenny Rice bring you the latest rankings, highlights and top news stories. Highlights include Kimbo Slice and Nick Diaz at EliteXC "Renegade" in Corpus Christi, World Cage Fighting in LA and Global Showdown in Oklahoma. Guests include MMA Fighter Justin McCully, Managing Editor of "The Fight Network," Loretta Hunt, and former WWF Champion Kurt Angle.

11.title: Episode #1.11
11.plot: Join hosts Bas Rutten and Kenny Rice for this special Thanksgiving episode. Previews include HDNet Fights, and WEC's upcoming events. Highlights include StrikeForce in San Jose, Rage in the Cage in Phoenix, and Master's of the Cage in Oklahoma City. Also, Kenny Rice sits down with Randy Couture in an exclusive interview.

12.title: Episode #1.12
12.plot: Hosts Bas Rutten and Kenny Rice bring you all the latest mixed martial arts news, rankings, and highlights. Guests include Sean Sherk the UFC Light Heavyweight Champion, currently appealing suspension for testing positive for steroids, Bob Pittman, Publisher of TapOut and MMA Worldwide Magazines, and Jason Miller, the headliner for HDNet Fights Reckless Abandon on December 15th in Dallas.

13.title: Episode #1.13
13.plot: Hosts Bas Rutten and Kenny Rice along with special guests MMA referee, "Doc" Hamilton, and Dave Doyle, Editor of Yahoo.com MMA discuss all the top stories and latest ranking. Also, from the news desk, Ron Kruck provides news and action packed highlights from around the globe.

14.title: Episode #1.14
14.plot: Join Bas Rutten and Kenny Rice as they discuss the top stories and upcoming events. Guests include MMA fighter and lead writer/editor for ProElite.com, Sam Caplan, Inside MMA #7 ranked welterweight, Karo Parisyan and MMA and Special Forces trainer, Amir Perets. Also, Ron Kruck provides the latest news and highlights from all over the country.

15.title: Episode #1.15
15.plot: Join Bas Rutten, Kenny Rice, and special guests, Writer for the Orange County Register, Carlos Arias, WEC Lightweight Champion Razor Rob McCullough, and Former Baseball superstar Jose Canseco, as they discuss the top stories and upcoming events. Also, join Ron Kruck for the latest news and best highlights from all over the country.

16.title: Episode #1.16
16.plot: Inside MMA goes on the road to Uncasville Connecticut, the site of the IFL Grand Prix. Special guests include MMA Legend, Ken Shamrock & IFL Commissioner, Kurt Otto. Also, a special interview with the World's Top Heavyweight Fedor Emelianenko.

6.title: Michael Bisping
6.plot: Inside MMA is your opportunity to step inside the world of mixed martial arts and find out what it takes to be a champion. Hosts Kenny Rice and Bas Rutten are joined by the sport's top fighters and news makers to discuss and analyze the latest in MMA. Plus event highlights, viewer mail, and Ron Kruck provides up to the minute news and features.

imdb.plot outline: MMA Legend Bas Rutten, Fight Master Kenny Rice, and Combat Correspondent Ron Kruck provide all the latest news, highlights, in-depth analysis and fighter rankings. Each week a guest panel of top experts and fighters provide insight into the current world of mixed martial arts.
